===Noun===
'''milk''' ([[uncountable]] and [[countable]]; plural: [[milks]])

#(''Uncountable'') A [[liquid]] secreted by the [[mammary gland]]s of [[mammal]]s to nourish the young.
#(''Countable'') An individual beverage of (1).
#:''I'll have a milk &mdash; in a dirty glass''!

